description:
VPRO Tegenlicht: De herovering van het nu

This episode of VPRO Tegenlicht was broadcast on April 13 2014 on Dutch public television and features a 45-minute monologue by Douglas Rushkoff about the topics in his latest book "Present Shock, When Everything Happens Now". 

More info (in Dutch): http://tegenlicht.vpro.nl/afleveringen/2013-2014/de-herovering-van-het-nu.html

This video was downloaded from the Dutch public television's web streaming service. Picture and audio quality isn't that great, but the content consists of mostly speech which is clearly audible.
